{"word":"G1553 - ἐκδημέω - ekdēméō - ek-day-meh'-o - Be absent","slug":"G1553","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκδημέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ekdēméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ek-day-meh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be absent"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BA;&#x03B4;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - ekde&#x0304;meo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ek-day-meh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G1218\">G1218</a>; to <i>emigrate</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>vacate</i> or <i>quit:</i> - be absent."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1218\">G1218</a>, <a href=\"#/G1736\">G1736</a>, <a href=\"#/G3927\">G3927</a>"}]}